 <br /><b><p align="left">How to enter Temperature </p></b>
<font size="2">
<p align="left">Temperature should be a positive number between 80 and 120. Decimal numbers are allowed.Please enter your temperature in degrees Fahrenheit. </p>
<p align="left">Some of the values for example are: </p>
<p align="left">98 Fahrenheit </p>
<p align="left">100.75 Fahrenheit </p>
</font>
<br/>	

<br /><b><p align="left">How to enter Blood Pressure </p></b>
<font size="2">
<p align="left">Blood Pressure "HIGH" value must be positive number. Decimal numbers are not accepted. BP-High should be greater than or equal to BP-Low. Please enter your BP-high value in millimeters of mercury.
</p>
<p align="left">Some of the values for example are: </p>
<p align="left">115  mmHg
 </p>
<p align="left">1130  mmHg
 </p>
</font>
<br/>	

<br /><b><p align="left">How to enter Blood Pressure </p></b>
<font size="2">
<p align="left">Blood Pressure "LOW" value must be positive number. Decimal numbers are not accepted. BP-High should be greater than or equal to BP-Low.Please enter your BP-Low value in millimeters of mercury.
</p>
<p align="left">Some of the values for example are: </p>
<p align="left">75 mmHg
 </p>
<p align="left">190 mmHg
 </p>
</font>
<br/>	

<br /><b><p align="left">How to enter Pulse Rate </p></b>
<font size="2">
<p align="left">Pulse Rate must be a positive number between 20 and 200. Decimal numbers are not accepted.Please enter your pulse rate in beats per minute.
</p>
<p align="left">Some of the values for example are: </p>
<p align="left">115 per minute
 </p>
<p align="left">80 per minute
 </p>
</font>
<br/>	

<br /><b><p align="left">How to enter Blood Glucose Level </p></b>
<font size="2">
<p align="left">This is an optional field, which means you can submit your health status report without providing value for this field.Glucose level must be a positive number between 20 and 300. Decimal numbers are not accepted.Please enter your blood sugar level in milligrams per deciliter. 
</p>
<p align="left">Some of the values for example are: </p>
<p align="left">110 mg / dl
 </p>
<p align="left">126 mg / dl
 </p>
</font>
<br/>	

